<div id="links">
<h2>Quelques liens</h2>

<ul>

<li><p><a href="http://www.w3.org/">W3C</a>.
<a href="http://validator.w3.org/">Validez vos pages web</a>.
Accessibilité: <a href="http://www.w3.org/WAI/"><acronym title="Web Accessibility Initiative">WAI</acronym></a>
(<a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/WAI-WEBCONTENT/" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Web Content Accessibility Guidelines</a>),
<a href="http://www.braillenet.org/accessibilite/">BrailleNet</a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Un article très intéressant d'Étienne Lavanant: <a href="http://www.apitux.org/index.php?2012/02/03/97-pourquoi-le-libre-ne-concerne-pas-que-les-informaticiens"><cite>Pourquoi le libre ne concerne pas que les informaticiens</cite></a>. Cet article cite notamment la <a href="http://www.easter-eggs.org/article_269_Lettre_de_M_Villanueva_a_Microsoft_Perou.html">lettre (traduite en français) de <abbr title="Monsieur">M.</abbr> Villanueva</a> (membre du Congrès de la République du Pérou) à Microsoft Pérou (<a href="http://aful.org/politique/perou/rescon-fr.html">autre traduction</a>).</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://www.acbm.com/"><cite class="journal">Le Virus Informatique</cite></a>.</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://www.ffii.org/" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Foundation for a Free Information Infrastructure (<acronym title="Foundation for a Free Information Infrastructure">FFII</acronym>)</a>. <a href="http://www.ffii.fr/"><acronym title="Foundation for a Free Information Infrastructure">FFII</acronym> France</a>.</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://www.april.org/"><acronym title="Association Pour la Promotion et la Recherche en Informatique Libre">APRIL</acronym></a>.</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://www.eff.org/" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Electronic Frontier Foundation</a>.</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://lesstandardsnumeriques.org/">Les Standards Numériques</a>, pour des standards numériques libres et ouverts.</p></li>

<li><p>Musique: <a href="http://www.lecouvent.org/">Les Chemins du Baroque / K617 (<cite>Le Couvent</cite>)</a>.</p></li>

<li><p><em lang="en" xml:lang="en"><acronym title="American Standard Code for Information Interchange">ASCII</acronym> art</em>:
<a href="http://www.ascii-art.com/">site de Joan Stark</a>,
<a href="http://r.webring.com/hub?ring=ascii" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><acronym title="American Standard Code for Information Interchange">ASCII</acronym> art webring</a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Les horaires <acronym title="Société nationale des chemins de fer français">SNCF</acronym>: allez sur le <a href="http://reiseauskunft.bahn.de/bin/query.exe/en">site de la <span lang="de" xml:lang="de">Deutsche Bahn</span></a> (<a href="http://reiseauskunft.bahn.de/bin/query.exe/el" title="version sans tables, pour Lynx">version sans tables</a>) - source HAFAS, et surtout pas sur celui de la <acronym title="Société nationale des chemins de fer français">SNCF</acronym> (sauf éventuellement pour réserver/acheter), qui est bien trop lourd.</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://www.eurobilltracker.com/index.php?referer=74"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">EuroBillTracker</span></a>: suivez vos billets d'euros à la trace.</p></li>

</ul>

</div><!-- links -->

<div id="search">
<h2>Quelques moteurs de recherche et bases de données</h2>

<ul>

<li><p>Web (général):
<a href="http://www.google.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Google</span></a> (le meilleur),
<a href="http://ecosia.org/"><span class="product service">Ecosia</span></a>,
<a href="http://duckduckgo.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">DuckDuckGo</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.exalead.fr/search"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Exalead</span></a>,
<a href="http://dmoz.org/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Open Directory Project (dmoz)</span></a>,
<a href="http://alltheweb.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">AlltheWeb.com</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.altavista.com/"><span class="product service">Alta Vista</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.bing.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Bing</span></a>,
<a href="http://channels.netscape.com/ns/search/default.jsp"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Netscape Search</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.yahoo.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Yahoo</span></a>,
<a href="http://vivisimo.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Vivísimo Clustering</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.kwmap.net/"><span class="product service">KwMap.net</span></a> (une carte de mots-clés pour tout l'Internet) et
<a href="http://truveo.com/"><span class="product service">Truveo</span></a> (vidéos uniquement).</p></li>

<li><p>Web francophone:
<a href="http://www.voila.fr/"><span class="product service">Voilà</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.weborama.fr/"><span class="product service">Weborama</span></a> et
<a href="http://fr.yahoo.com/"><span class="product service">Yahoo France</span></a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Archives:
<a href="http://www.archive.org/"><cite lang="en" xml:lang="en">Internet Archive</cite></a> (avec sa machine à remonter le temps, des films tombés dans le domaine public, <abbr>etc.</abbr>) et
<a href="http://www.webcitation.org/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">WebCite</span></a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Marque-page (favoris): <a href="http://del.icio.us/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">del.icio.us</span></a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Blogs (et certains forums): <a href="http://www.feedster.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Feedster</span></a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Images: <a href="http://www.tineye.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">TinEye</span></a> (recherche par image);
<a href="http://en.topictures.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Topictures</span></a> (meta-moteur de recherche pour les images, recherche par texte).</p></li>

<li><p><span lang="en" xml:lang="en">News (USENET)</span>:
<a href="http://groups.google.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Google</span></a>
(<a href="http://groups.google.com/advanced_search">recherche avancée</a>).</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://www.faqs.org/faqs/"><acronym title="Foires Aux Questions">FAQ</acronym></a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Articles et prépublications (math, informatique, physique, etc.):
<a href="http://citeseer.ist.psu.edu/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">CiteSeer.IST Scientific Literature Digital Library</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.scientificcommons.org/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Scientific Commons</span></a>.</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://liinwww.ira.uka.de/bibliography/index.html" title="bibliographie, page principale">Bibliographie: page principale (Allemagne)</a>;
miroirs:
<a href="http://www.cs.toronto.edu/pub/mirror/bibliography/" title="bibliographie, miroir">Canada</a>,
<a href="http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/mirrors/bibliography/index.html" title="bibliographie, miroir">Australie</a>.</p></li>

<li><p><a href="http://latexsearch.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">LaTeX Search</span></a> (équations mathématiques dans les publications scientifiques).</p></li>

<li><p>Math:
<a href="http://oldweb.cecm.sfu.ca/projects/ISC/">constantes (<span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Inverse Symbolic Calculator</span>)</a>
et <a href="http://oeis.org/">suites entières</a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Logiciels libres:
<a href="http://directory.fsf.org/" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><acronym title="Free Software Foundation">FSF</acronym>/<acronym title="United Nations Education, Scientific and Cultural Organization">UNESCO</acronym> Free Software Directory</a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Sources de logiciels:
<a href="http://opensearch.krugle.org/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Krugle</span></a>,
<a href="http://code.ohloh.net/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Ohloh Code</span></a>,
<a href="http://codesearch.debian.net/" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Debian Code Search</a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Pages <cite class="prg" lang="en" xml:lang="en">man</cite> de divers systèmes d'exploitation:
<a href="http://www.freebsd.org/cgi/man.cgi"><cite lang="en" xml:lang="en">FreeBSD Hypertext Man Pages</cite></a>.</p></li>

<li><p><acronym title="Requests For Comments">RFC</acronym>:
<a href="http://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc.html">site <span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en"><acronym title="Request For Comments">RFC</acronym> Editor</span></a> et
<a href="http://www.faqs.org/rfcs/">site <span class="product service">FAQS.ORG</span></a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Cinéma:
<a href="http://akas.imdb.com/"><acronym title="Internet Movie Database">IMDb</acronym>.com</a>
(<a href="http://akas.imdb.com/search/">page de recherche</a>, et
<a href="http://www.imdb.fr/"><acronym title="Internet Movie Database">IMDb</acronym>.fr</a>,
qui a moins d'information que <acronym title="Internet Movie Database">IMDb</acronym>.com) et
<a href="http://www.lesgensducinema.com/entree.php">Les Gens du cinéma</a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Formats de fichiers: <a href="http://www.wotsit.org/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Wotsit</span></a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Extensions de fichiers:
<a href="http://dotwhat.net/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">DotWhat</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.fileinfo.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">FileInfo.com</span></a>,
<a href="http://filext.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">FILExt</span></a> et
<a href="http://www.file-extensions.org/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">File-Extensions.org</span></a>.</p></li>

<li><p>Cartes:
<a href="http://www.maporama.com/"><span class="product service">maporama.com</span></a> (monde),
<a href="http://maps.yahoo.com/"><span class="product service">Yahoo</span></a> (<acronym title="United States of America">USA</acronym>, Canada) et
<a href="http://www.mappy.com/"><span class="product service">mappy.com</span></a> (Europe).</p></li>

<li><p>Dictionnaires, encyclopédies:
<a href="http://fr.wikipedia.org/">Wikipédia</a>,
<a href="http://fr.wiktionary.org/">Wiktionnaire</a>,
<a href="http://www.answers.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Answers.com</span></a>,
<a href="http://www.dict.org/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">dict.org</span></a> et
<a href="http://www.dictionarist.com/"><span class="product service" lang="en" xml:lang="en">Dictionarist.com</span></a>.</p></li>

</ul>

